{"tid":406294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社聯伙拍26位業主推房屋共享協會基層解決住屋問題","createTime":"2017-09-19T13:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T00:10:25.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0746e60022509803f6cd05c274cc9ef07681ef8c","tid":406294,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"社聯推出為期三年的「社會房屋共享計劃」，為基層提供過渡性房屋，目前有332個單位可供租用。<br />\n<br />\n「社會房屋共享計劃」對象是已輪候公屋最少三年、住在不適切住房或低收入人士，提供住宿和支援服務，現階段有26位業主提供332個單位，預計年底推出至少34個，其餘會在明年上半年陸續推出。<br />\n<br />\n社聯預計有1000個家庭受惠，租金介乎綜援租金津貼的最高金額及公屋租金，同時參考房委會租金援助計劃，水平不會超過租戶入息四分之一，租用期限一般不少於兩年。香港公益金捐出5000萬支持單位裝修費等開支。<br />\n<br />\n社聯會負責招募業主及安排勘察，並初步估算所需的維修費用，而單位人均面積會參考現時公屋的水平。"},{"pid":"d49d92a2f551737308f62ef2cc7ddde4be5b5947","tid":406294,"uid":8511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"屌你26 個人有300 個單位？<br />\n<br />\n一人最少有10個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c39d487f3b1c72380e18fad6aa6da38955e5bc1","tid":406294,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"杯水車薪"},{"pid":"07de520a68a88eb86d7fc4f5fafc03486a22a66c","tid":406294,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"Ching係其中一個業主"},{"pid":"7d401fd2a4600c13931cdb4b19d888ab779ff31a","tid":406294,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭做到野 話咁快解決到基層住屋問題"},{"pid":"da52def4ee66dbd401ed181a2b2234d5c52afaa5","tid":406294,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"拎個等緊重建既單位出黎, 又有人幫你裝修埋, 又有租收"},{"pid":"66ac279707bba2b2f4cb870867d3e0e7d883daca","tid":406294,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"林鄭最終目標係咪想超越巴西<br />\n<img src=\"https://media3.s-nbcnews.com/j/newscms/2016_31/1652261/favela-rio-ejo-080316_6b63131061ea99e6f915a05c7fb159c7.nbcnews-ux-2880-1000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.s-nbcnews.com%2Fj%2Fnewscms%2F2016_31%2F1652261%2Ffavela-rio-ejo-080316_6b63131061ea99e6f915a05c7fb159c7.nbcnews-ux-2880-1000.jpg&h=c499b537&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db8d840731afa9fce80120b087d4370338aeb859","tid":406294,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭做到野 話咁快解決到基層住屋問題</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母咪又係抄一個叫「光房」既project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋一早做緊將閒置空間轉做共住房屋既野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府又抄startup野爆係自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd29d92c0db82d517e2cd58000eefbf1d0018139","tid":406294,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:09:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e1ca982ae8384062d412e5971c183129f7e26bb","tid":406294,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你26 個人有300 個單位？<br />\n<br />\n一人最少有10個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n300個，真係解決晒房屋問題呀"}]}